INVENTORY MANAGEMENT MANUAL
Purpose: This manual outlines procedures for managing inventory across all branches of
Challenge Enterprises of Ghana. Stock Receipt: All received stock must be recorded in the inventory system immediately
upon arrival. Stock Issuance: Items released for sale or distribution must be properly documented. Stock Reconciliation: Weekly stock checks shall be conducted and discrepancies reported. Reporting: Branch managers must submit inventory reports every Friday. Responsibilities: Warehouse and Inventory staff are responsible for maintaining accurate
stock records.
